        "subject": "LU-4367 open: fetch open lock by default",
        "message": "LU-4367 open: fetch open lock by default\n\nenable MDS_OPEN_LOCK by default, this can improve performance\na lot for certain situations, because upon close locks on this\nfile won't be canceled.\n\nopen also fetches MDS_UPDATE_LOCK/MDS_PERM_LOCK, along with\nabove change cached lock is more efficient.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I90a195ff4ded49acefaf07f816b69e38c74e873d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
